Description: # logger_rewrite
        Easy way to log everything
        ### Install
        ```bash
        pip install logger_rewrite
        ```
        
        ### Use
        ```bash
        from logger_rewrite import setup_log
        logger = setup_log(save_dir='saved')
        logger.info('Hello world')
        ```
        
